---
// You can pass a background image as a prop later, 
// but for now, we will use a stunning placeholder of the valley/mountains.
---

<section class="relative w-full h-screen min-h-[700px] flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center px-[5%] overflow-hidden bg-tierra-madre">
  
  <div 
    class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat"
    style="background-image: url('https://picsum.photos/1920/1080?random=2');"
  >
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-tierra-madre/80 via-tierra-madre/60 to-tierra-madre"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center max-w-5xl mt-16 md:mt-24">
    
    <span class="font-title text-agua-pura tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-6 text-sm md:text-base border-b-2 border-agua-pura pb-2 inline-block">
      The Seed of Taita Miguel Angel Muchavisoy
    </span>

    <h1 class="font-title text-5xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl lg:text-[100px] text-fibra-natural uppercase tracking-wider leading-none drop-shadow-[4px_4px_0_#f6007b] mb-8">
      Weaving<br/>Ancestral Peace
    </h1>

    <p class="font-body text-lg md:text-2xl text-fibra-natural/90 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed mb-12 drop-shadow-[1px_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)]">
      Expanding a sacred sanctuary of medicine, art, and community in the Sibundoy Valley. Hand-seeded by the late Taita Miguel and brought to life by his family to share with the world.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-8 w-full sm:w-auto">
      
      <button 
        id="hero-donate-btn"
        class="bg-padre-sol text-tierra-madre font-title text-xl uppercase px-10 py-4 border-2 border-padre-sol shadow-[6px_6px_0_#f6007b] hover:bg-sangre-viva hover:text-fibra-natural hover:border-sangre-viva hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0_#00d2d3] hover:translate-x-[-2px] hover:translate-y-[-2px] transition-all duration-300 select-none cursor-pointer"
      >
        Support the Sanctuary
      </button>

      <a 
        href="#video" 
        class="bg-transparent text-fibra-natural font-title text-xl uppercase px-10 py-4 border-2 border-fibra-natural shadow-[6px_6px_0_#161a18] hover:bg-fibra-natural hover:text-tierra-madre hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0_#00d2d3] hover:translate-x-[-2px] hover:translate-y-[-2px] transition-all duration-300 flex justify-center items-center select-none cursor-pointer"
      >
        Watch Our Video
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-sangre-viva via-padre-sol via-agua-pura to-sangre-viva z-20"></div>
  
</section>
